<paragraph blockId="34.[151,1437,1012,1333]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,368,1052,1077]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Identification.</emphasis>
Cleaned test white with dark pore zones, apical disc black, interambulacra median zone purplish, tubercles head violet. Color in life black to dark purple, fairly short spines, longest around the equator.
</paragraph>
